1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Bg5 h6!? { A rare move that lots of players will be unprepared for } 5. Bxf6 (5. Bh4? g5 6. Bg3 dxe4 { [%cal Gc7c5,Gb8c6] }) 5... Qxf6 6. exd5 Bb4! 7. dxe6 Bxe6 { Black has full compensation for the pawn! } { [%cal Gc7c5,Ge8g8,Gb8c6,Ga8d8] } *


